   drand BN254 verifier prototype for Solana that predates Alea. Uses
   an off-chain hinting architecture (SDK computes SVDW, program
   verifies hints + pairing only); Alea implements the full on-chain
   SVDW approach. Credited as prior art per ADR 0024.

